quran[13{c,v,t}:
72,1,( ae paighambar logon se ) keh do ke mere paas wahi aayi hai ke junoo ki aik jamaat ne ( is kitaab ko ) suna to kehnay lagey ke hum ne aik ajeeb quran suna
72,2,jo bhalai ka rasta batata hai so hum is par imaan le aeye. aur hum apne perwar-digaar ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi banayen ge
72,3,aur yeh ke hamaray perwar-digaar ki Azmat ( shaan ) bohat barri hai aur woh nah biwi rakhta hai nah aulaad
72,4,aur yeh ke hum mein se baaz be waqoof khuda ke baray mein jhoot iftira karta hai
72,5,aur hamara ( yeh ) khayaal tha ke ensaan aur jin khuda ki nisbat jhoot nahi boltay
72,6,aur yeh ke baaz bani aadam baaz jaanat ki panah pakra karte they ( is se ) un ki sar kashi aur barh gayi thi
72,7,aur yeh ke un ka bhi yahi aitqaad tha jis terhan tumhara tha ke khuda kisi ko nahi jalaaye ga
72,8,aur yeh ke hum ne aasman ko tatola to is ko mazboot chokedaron aur angaron se se bhara paaya
72,9,aur yeh ke pehlay hum wahan bohat se maqamat mein ( khabrain ) suneney ke liye betha karte they. ab koi sunna chahay to apne liye angara tayyar paye
72,10,aur yeh ke hamein maloom nahi ke is se ahal zameen ke haq mein buraiee maqsood hai ya un ke perwar-digaar ne un ki bhalai ka iradah farmaya hai
72,11,aur yeh ke hum mein koi naik hain aur koi aur terhan ke. hamaray kayi terhan ke mazhab hain
72,12,aur yeh ke hum ne yaqeen karliya hai ke hum zameen mein ( khuwa kahin hon ) khuda ko hara nahi satke aur nah bhaag kar is ko thaka satke hain
72,13,aur jab hum ne hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) suni is par imaan le aeye. to jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar par imaan lata hai is ko nah nuqsaan ka khauf hai nah zulm ka
